00:05:58.520 --> 00:06:00.320
I got it.

00:06:02.633 --> 00:06:09.099
I have no idea why, but did you talk it over?

00:06:11.020 --> 00:06:17.653
Soma-kun, you're frosty, but protect your girlfriend.

00:06:21.368 --> 00:06:25.713
Of course. I promise not to make her sad again.

00:06:26.915 --> 00:06:28.286
