Th-Then once this is all over...

00:16:36.986 --> 00:16:39.686
No, I won't go back, never.

00:16:39.686 --> 00:16:42.053
What? You're not?

00:16:42.053 --> 00:16:47.586
That's right. I'll keep pursuing this job here.

00:16:47.586 --> 00:16:54.186
With Kotori-san, I'll build a mind-blowing site.

00:16:55.453 --> 00:17:00.520
So this job was for my benefit, too.

00:17:00.520 --> 00:17:06.960
I wanted to show my family my pride in my work.

00:17:07.620 --> 00:17:11.487
I'll repay them that way, as my brother said.

00:17:13.800 --> 00:17:17.535
Thank you for telling me.

00:17:17.535 --> 00:17:22.035
That honestly makes me very happy.

00:17:23.219 --> 00:17:28.040
You didn't do your best only for me,

00:17:28.040 --> 00:17:31.680
but for your own sake as well.

00:17:32.610 --> 00:17:37.752
I want us each to have our own goals

00:17:37.752 --> 00:17:42.752
and support each other through the process,

00:17:42.752 --> 00:17:44.952
for the rest of our lives.

00:17:48.550 --> 00:17:53.886
You warm me when I'm cold; I'll cool you when you're hot.

00:17:55.250 --> 00:17:57.752
