00:19:11.244 --> 00:19:15.540
Though he was raised in the same household,

00:19:15.540 --> 00:19:19.810
why was he given more freedom?

00:19:19.810 --> 00:19:23.700
I found myself wishing for that freedom.

00:19:25.010 --> 00:19:30.152
Now we've received orders from clients nationwide.

00:19:30.152 --> 00:19:34.119
