00:22:13.850 --> 00:22:19.019
But listen, Soma! I'm coming on this trip with you!

00:22:19.019 --> 00:22:21.186
You won't lay a finger on her.

00:22:21.186 --> 00:22:22.652
Hey...

00:22:22.652 --> 00:22:25.619
Sure, go ahead. Right, Kotori-san?

00:22:32.710 --> 00:22:35.652
Another day, another amazing tea.

00:22:35.652 --> 00:22:38.852
You think they'll bring back steamed sweet buns?

00:22:38.852 --> 00:22:41.552
I want to go see the Northern Lights.

00:22:41.552 --> 00:22:44.786
Maybe I'll go camping.

00:22:44.786 --> 00:22:46.886
I recommend Yamanashi Prefecture.

00:22:46.886 --> 00:22:48.519
Oh, the lakes, right?

00:22:48.519 --> 00:22:50.019
No reservation needed.

00:22:50.019 --> 00:22:53.419
- Oh yes, they're the best!
- The best, right?

00:22:53.419 --> 00:22:54.852
- I want to go, too!
- Me, too!

00:22:54.852 --> 00:22:56.410
Take us.

00:22:56.410 --> 00:22:58.710
